Description:
    Creates a new basic Azure App Service Mobile App

Options:
    Jasmine or Mocha for testing

Example:
    yo azure-mobile-apps

    This will create:
        Standard Project Files
            .gitignore
            jsconfig.json
            package.json

        Application Files
            bin/www
            server/app.js
            server/logger.js

        Example Controllers
            server/tables/example.js
            server/api/example.js

        Tests
            test/app.js
            test/logger.js

    You can use NPM commands to run the server:
        npm start   Starts the server
        npm test    Runs the tests
